Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory280.png'}
{3: 'The two ivory figures clash in mid-air, striking each other with incomprehensible speed.'}
{3: 'Just the energy spilled from their attacks has left frightening marks on the surrounding cliffs.'}
{3: 'But Luna has the upper hand the whole time, taking the high ground in their duel before knocking the creature to the ground, creating a massive crater.'}
{3: 'Although she manages to defeat the Hetero-Creature, Luna has to spend a considerable amount of effort to do so.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Gabriel', 3: 'How remarkable... Miss Luna is truly second to none.', 4: '2'}
{3: "Silently, Luna looks at her hands. Despite not needing to use her full strength, her opponent's power level far has exceeded what she imagined. And..."}
{2: 'Luna', 3: '(The power from Ascension-Network is weakening...)', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Gabriel', 3: 'But, Miss Luna, your fight has yet to end...', 4: '2'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgCg/Cg1601_2.jpg'}
{3: "The pale creature rises within the ashes. It fully expands its wings with merely a scratch on its body, creating an oppressive feeling that rivals Luna's."}
{2: 'Luna', 3: '...Pretty resilient.'}
{3: "A blinding red light converges on the Hetero-Creature's hand, while Luna also raises her hand and releases a ray of crimson laser."}
{3: 'The two rays collide, warp, and expand, almost leveling the depths of this canyon.'}
{3: 'Soon, the two beams merge and devour each other. Luna struggles but manages to maintain an edge over the Hetero-Creature, leaving it consumed by the energy blast, fallen to the ground.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png'}

{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiNoiseNew.prefab'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lamia', 3: 'What the... How dare he do that to Miss Luna...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "What happens to Luna if she's devoured?!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lamia', 3: "I-I wouldn't know...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'We have to get to the Polyphage first.', 3: '38'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Mermaid, you know the path, so lead the way.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lamia', 3: 'How can I walk any faster, all tied up like this? Free my tail at the very least...', 4: '1'}
{3: "Lee sighs and unties the wires on Lamia's lower body."}
{2: 'Lamia', 3: 'Oh, lovely! Commandant, you really are a good person.', 4: '1'}
{2: '...', 3: '48', 4: 'Maybe we should keep her tied up.', 5: '49'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Enough with this. Start moving.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lamia', 3: "Oh no no no noâ€”I'll keep my mouth shut!", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Lamia looks resigned and sighs, but then she breaks into a wide grin as if recalling something.'}
{2: 'Lamia', 3: "Heh... Follow me... It's up ahead!", 4: '1'}
